{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Storage.clear()","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/clear","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Web_Storage_API\">Web Storage API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage\"><code>Storage</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/length\"><code>length</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><em><code>clear()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/getItem\"><code>getItem()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/key\"><code>key()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/removeItem\"><code>removeItem()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/setItem\"><code>setItem()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Web Storage API に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StorageEvent\"><code>StorageEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window/localStorage\"><code>Window.localStorage</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window/sessionStorage\"><code>Window.sessionStorage</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong><code>clear()</code></strong> は <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage\"><code>Storage</code></a> インターフェイスのメソッドで、指定された <code>Storage</code> オブジェクトに格納されているすべてのキーを消去します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"構文","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">storage.clear();\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返値","title":"返値","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/undefined\"><code>undefined</code></a> です。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下の関数はローカルストレージに 3 個のデータアイテムを作成して、 <code>clear()</code> を使用してすべて削除します。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">populateStorage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'bgcolor'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'red'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'font'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Helvetica'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'image'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'miGato.png'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">clear</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> 実際の例としては、 <a href=\"https://mdn.github.io/dom-examples/web-storage/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Storage Demo</a> をご覧ください。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","val